ocratic ex-Sen. Sherrod Brown and Republican Sen. Jon Husted will face off in a big general election.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2025-05/250519-Vivek-Ramaswamy-mb-1632-f7fadd.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Scott W. Grau</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Monday&#39;s Campaign Round-Up, 5.19.25: Ramaswamy’s path becomes even easier in Ohio</media:text><media:description type="plain">Democratic ex-Sen. Sherrod Brown and Republican Sen. Jon Husted will face off in a big general election.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-04/260409-Amy-Acton-ew-1042p-790470.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Stephen Zenner</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Democratic Gubernatorial Candidate Acton Campaigns In Columbus</media:text><media:description type="plain">Democratic ex-Sen. Sherrod Brown and Republican Sen. Jon Husted will face off in a big general election.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-04/260427-split-brown-husted-mb-0902-60b960.jpg" height="800" width="1200"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 00:00:02 GMT</pubDate><title>&#39;Ohio is back&#39;: Both parties navigate competitive midterm races in a forgotten battleground</title><updateDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 00:00:02 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Henry J. Gomez</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Tue, 05 May 2026 23:38:54 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Businessman Vivek Ramaswamy has won Ohio’s Republican primary for governor, NBC News projects, advancing to what could be an expensive and competitive general election with Democrat Amy Acton in a state that has been brutal for Democrats in recent elections.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2026-election/vivek-ramaswamy-wins-gop-primary-governor-ohio-amy-acton-rcna343048</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2026-election/vivek-ramaswamy-wins-gop-primary-governor-ohio-amy-acton-rcna343048</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260505-vivek-ramaswamy-vsb-2014-edeb08.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Carolyn Kaster</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Vivek Ramaswamy</media:text><media:description type="plain">Republican Ohio gubernatorial candidate Vivek speaks during a watch party at the Spruce St. Sporting sports bar after winning the party&#39;s nomination for governor Tuesday, May 5, 2026, in Columbus.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260505-vivek-ramaswamy-vsb-2014-edeb08.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 23:38:54 GMT</pubDate><title>Vivek Ramaswamy wins GOP nomination for governor in Ohio</title><updateDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 00:20:30 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Henry J. Gomez</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Tue, 05 May 2026 23:38:01 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Former Sen. Sherrod Brown has won the Democratic nomination in Ohio’s special Senate election, NBC News projects, paving the way for a nationally watched general election matchup against Republican incumbent Jon Husted</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2026-election/sherrod-brown-wins-ohio-senate-democratic-primary-jon-husted-rcna343049</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2026-election/sherrod-brown-wins-ohio-senate-democratic-primary-jon-husted-rcna343049</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260505-Sherrod-Brown-vsb-2025-19efa8.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Sue Ogrocki</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Sherrod Brown</media:text><media:description type="plain">Democratic Ohio Senate candidate Sherrod Brown, a former three-term U.S. senator, speaks at a primary election night campaign event after winning the party&#39;s primary for US Senate in Cleveland, Tuesday, May 5, 2026.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260505-Sherrod-Brown-vsb-2025-19efa8.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 23:38:01 GMT</pubDate><title>Sherrod Brown wins Democratic Senate nomination in Ohio, setting up a key battleground race</title><updateDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 23:38:01 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Steve Kopack</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Wed, 06 May 2026 10:24:31 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>The price of oil plunged and markets surged early Wednesday after a new report that the U.S. believed it was nearing a deal to end the war with Iran and eventually reopen the Strait of Hormuz.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/business/business-news/oil-markets-gas-prices-450-us-iran-near-deal-end-war-hormuz-rcna343819</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/business/business-news/oil-markets-gas-prices-450-us-iran-near-deal-end-war-hormuz-rcna343819</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260505-Hormuz-ch-1310-f9def1.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Amirhosein Khorgooi</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Vessels in the Strait of Hormuz near Bandar Abbas, Iran</media:text><media:description type="plain">Vessels in the Strait of Hormuz near Bandar Abbas, Iran, on May 4, 2026.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-04/260318-gas-pumps-iran-16x9-vl-1109-791060.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="844" width="1500"><media:credit>Hannah Beier for NBC News</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Wholesale gas prices dropped 5% following the Axios report.</media:text><media:description type="plain">Wholesale gas prices dropped 5% following the Axios report.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260505-Hormuz-ch-1310-f9def1.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 10:24:31 GMT</pubDate><title>Price of oil plunges and markets surge on report U.S. and Iran near deal to end war</title><updateDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 11:05:52 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Tue, 05 May 2026 23:15:38 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>The cruise ship where several passengers have died from the Hantavirus will head to the Canary Islands after a medical evacuation of the symptomatic people on board. NBC News’ Camila Bernal reports.</description><expires>2056-05-05T23:14:47.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">nn_cbe_hantavirus_cruise_passengers_260505</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/nightly-news/video/evacuation-plan-for-cruise-ship-with-deadly-virus-on-board-262809157624</link><media:content url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nn_cbe_hantavirus_cruise_passengers_260505/1/abs/index.m3u8" medium="video"><media:credit></media:credit><media:title>Evacuation plan for cruise ship with deadly virus on board</media:title><media:player url="https://www.nbcnews.com/nightly-news/video/evacuation-plan-for-cruise-ship-with-deadly-virus-on-board-262809157624"></media:player><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1778022877792_nn_cbe_hantavirus_cruise_passengers_260505_S3_1920x1080-lu6oey.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media